  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="3489769836">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-3489769836" class="vote-count">0</span>
              <a id="btn-3489769836" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="3489769836">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/84242936/">ฅ՞ﻌ՞ฅ</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/3489769836">2022-10-11 19:57:36</a>
          <span class="comment-location">天津</span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">血观音中应酬的场景很像前文，后面人生的一些感悟，尤其是写作是自己努力的事情蛮有启发</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1341035/?comment_id=3489769836"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

      </ul>
  </div>

        

    </div>
        <p>&gt; <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1341035/comments/">更多短评 764 条</a></p>
